{
  "stem": "717.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember that was a big blow for our family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My mother was a housewife and a seamstress.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She used to work for ladies and children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember she used to make children's suits, blouses, all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember her sewing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There's one sound left in my head.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When she put that thimble on and she was sewing, I remember the thimble and the ring she had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Of course, the wedding ring, and she had another ring next to it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when she was sewing, I remember the thimble knocking against the rings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that sound I still remember, just like I remember the smell of my father's paintbrushes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When he was taken away in 1940 to the camp, he left me in charge of his paintbrushes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He told me how to soak them, how to clean them, so when he comes back, he could still use them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I remember the smell of the paint always in my nose.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was born, if I remember correctly-- they were talking with-- in 1897.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember the month.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember the birthday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father was born in 1899.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember my grandparents, both my grandparents, very vividly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With my maternal grandparents, we lived the first year or the first few months in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they lived in Balut, which is the section of town that was cordoned off for the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We lived in town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we moved in with them until we got our own apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My-- their name was Morvitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Joseph Morvitz was my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't remember my grandmother's first name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a, a printer on cloths.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He printed materials.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
